column5: What kind of fishing pressure would one expect in the southern section of WFB (Vic and Dots area) as well as the middle section of WFB? I primarily would be musky fishing, but am curious about all the boat traffic one would see in July. thanks!
You don't have to worry to much about other boats over there. Actually you probably won't see too many.
Thanks! How is the multispecies fishing in the southern part? I would have my 2 girls with me
